
Extra Mile is Chevrons premier brand of 24 hour convenience store. The only Extra Mile store in Davis is located at the Chevron on Chiles Road in East Davis. The store features all of the standard convenience store items along with prepared sandwiches, ICEEs, sodas, and many different flavors of Seattles Best Coffee. They previously used Van Houtte coffee. There is also an Allpoint Network ATMs ATM located inside of the store. There is a car wash at this location along with gas stations gas pumps.


